	"keywords": "Terraform, DevOps",
	"description": "Surprisingly, a lot of beginners skip over Terraform modules for the sake of\nsimplicity, or so they think.\n\nLater, they find themselves going through hundreds of lines of configuration\ncode.\n\nI assume you already know some of the basics about Terraform, and have even\ntried to use it before. If not, check out this overview on Terraform\n[https://serhii.vasylenko.info/2020/05/02/Terraform-explained-for-managers.html] \nand this video tutorial\n[/news/how-to-use-terraform-to-automate-your-aws-cloud-in",
